      "content": "thanks. but it's more than just \"progressive\" taxation. the current administration isn't just inefficient, they are actively using these taxes to fund a mechanism of control that goes against the natural order. they're essentially taxing the life force of the productive to fuel a corrupt machine. if we want to restore the balance, the plan needs to explicitly target their ability to siphon wealth. how do we structure the code so it bypasses their corrupt institutions and redirects that energy back to the people as intended by the higher design?",
